From d41d9bc697416e4cee313ffda28299f9681693c3 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Achin Gupta <achin.gupta@arm.com>
Date: Tue, 2 Nov 2021 10:18:47 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] ArmPkg: Add support for FFA_MEM_PERM_GET/SET ABIs

This patch uses the FFA_MEM_PERM_GET/SET ABIs to tweak the permissions of a set
of pages if FF-A v1.1 and above is supported by the SPMC. For FF-A v1.0 the
previous method through FFA_MSG_SEND_DIRECT_REQ/RESP is used.

Signed-off-by: Achin Gupta <achin.gupta@arm.com>
Signed-off-by: Nishant Sharma <nishant.sharma@arm.com>
Change-Id: I4e8c424c7f215b7003b114379aa855f7cb241455
---
 ArmPkg/Include/IndustryStandard/ArmFfaSvc.h   |   2 +
 .../ArmMmuStandaloneMmLib.c                   | 130 ++++++++++++++++--
 2 files changed, 118 insertions(+), 14 deletions(-)

